arts.ttl: Freiburg withstand late Wolfsburg surge in thrilling 3-2 victory
arts.sum: The physical nature of the match was evident early on, with Lukas Kübler and Michael Gregoritsch both receiving yellow cards for Freiburg in the first half. In the 42nd minute, Kübler capitalised on a corner kick situation, firing home from close range to give the hosts a 1-0 lead heading into the break.

arts.ttl: Kübler bags brace as Freiburg move past Wolfsburg
arts.sum: SC Freiburg move above Wolfsburg into fifth place in the Bundesliga table after a 3-2 home win over Die Wölfe.

arts.ttl: UWCL talking points: Wolfsburg thrash Roma; all too predictable?
arts.sum: Emily Keogh, Sophie Lawson and Sam Marsden answer some of our burning questions after the fifth round of games in this season's Champions League.

arts.ttl: Freiburg vs. Wolfsburg preview: Visitors targeting another win
arts.sum: Wolfsburg will look to claim a sixth consecutive victory in all competitions when they travel to the Europa-Park Stadion for Friday’s Bundesliga clash with Freiburg.
Germany's Kicker Magazine reports that VfL Wolfsburg have interest in picking up Freiburg fullback Kiliann Sildillia.

arts.ttl: Preview: Freiburg vs. Wolfsburg - prediction, team news, lineups
arts.sum: Sports Mole previews Friday's Bundesliga clash between Freiburg and Wolfsburg, including predictions, team news and possible lineups.
